I don't know wtf some landlords are thinking. My landlord tried increasing rent more this year than it has in past years and we're in the middle of a pandemic. You have tenants not able to pay so you try to gouge the ones who can?

&amp;#x200B;

Sorry bubs you don't have negotiating power anymore. I'm the captain now.

No matter how badly you're feeling right now.

&amp;#x200B;

It will get worse.
